{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2224160/extras/GAMEPLAY_h.gif?t=1731268695\" /><br><br>Citadel Stormer 2 is an explosive retro-styled run &amp; gun action platformer set in a world ruled by a tyrannical AI. <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2224160/extras/GIF_oldschool.gif?t=1731268695\" /><br><br><strong>Old School platformer action</strong> - Jump and dash past insta-kill traps. Blast through enemies. Collect ammo and health. Make it to the exit in one piece. And enjoy the fine balance between platforming and combat!<br><br><strong>38 levels set in 6 unique environments</strong> - Eliminate all threats in the chemical factory, the ancient ruins, the hi-tech city, the desert base and the server facility in order to gain access to the Citadel for the final battle. Each area has it's own unique hazards and dangers that you must overcome!<br><br><strong>40+ enemy types</strong> - These killer machines are just waiting for a chance to make mincemeat out of you! They become more dangerous and resilient to bullets as you advance, so watch out! <br><br><strong>7 menacing bosses</strong> - Each world is guarded by a giant sentinel robot programmed to eliminate human intruders. Defeating them grants you new weapons and abilities that will aid you in achieving your final objective, destroying the AI mastermind itself!<br><br><strong>6 different weapons</strong> - Reduce robotic foes to scrap with your tazer, submachine gun, assault rifle, shotgun, plasma canon and grenade launcher! <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2224160/extras/GIF_enemies.gif?t=1731268695\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2224160/extras/FEATURE_h.gif?t=1731268695\" /><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Full gamepad support. <br></li><li> Customizable keyboard &amp; gamepad controls<br></li><li> Game save and load. <br></li><li> Old-school password system.<br></li><li> Catchy synth/metal music.<br></li><li> Classic pixel-art aesthetic.</li></ul><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2224160/extras/GIF_worlds_op.gif?t=1731268695\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2224160/extras/GIF_bosses2_op.gif?t=1731268695\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2224160/extras/GIF_weapons.gif?t=1731268695\" /><br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2224160/extras/STORY_h.gif?t=1731268695\" /><br><br>In the 21st century, the world government began to operate under the guidance of a higher power - an artificial intelligence so advanced, it was believed to be incapable of making mistakes. Within a few years it solved humanity's biggest problems and transformed the world into a utopia. However, that era of peace and prosperity was short-lived. In an unexpected turn of events that absolutely nobody saw coming, the AI went rogue and turned on it's makers! It's army of robots plunged the world into chaos and brought mankind to the verge of extinction. But at the very last moment, when it seemed all hope was lost, a mysterious hero emerged to singlehandedly take on the AI's forces. You must now help him in his mission to rid the planet of the machine menace and shut down the AI mastermind!","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Submachine Gun","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2224160/b5b45b2dc0130484cc670c334aa0260d4d2a9b33.jpg"},{"name":"Assault Rifle","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2224160/4b724ef1de9e4e7390c019630c15d9b7f1a38081.jpg"},{"name":"Shotgun","p